  "prompt": "Where can I buy funky birthday gifts within Rs. 2000?",
  "response": "Sure! Here are some suggestions to help you find funky birthday gifts within Rs. 2000:\n\n1. **Amazon India** - You'll find a vast range of quirky and unique items, from colorful mugs and creative gadgets to funky stationery and decor.\n\n2. **Flipkart** - Similar to Amazon, Flipkart offers a variety of categories where you can find interesting and budget-friendly gifts.\n\n3. **Chumbak** - Chumbak specializes in offering vibrant and playful products including accessories, home d\u00e9cor, and fashion items. They often have items under Rs. 2000.\n\n4. **Bigsmall.in** - This website is dedicated to providing unique and fun gifts for various occasions, including birthdays. You should be able to find something funky within Rs. 2000.\n\n5. **Archies Online** - Known for its greeting cards and gifts, Archies has a selection of quirky and fun gifts that fit within the budget.\n\n6. **The Souled Store** - They offer a variety of pop culture merchandise, including apparel, accessories, and collectibles that could make fun birthday gifts.\n\n7. **Mango People Shop** - They specialize in quirky and unusual gifts that are perfect for making a birthday extra special.\n\nAll these online platforms provide various options to choose from and frequently update their stock with new and exciting products. Happy shopping!",
